{"type": "normal", "rawDescription": "【大堂，夜】", "location": "大堂", "timeOfDay": "夜", "performances": [{"type": "action", "description": "雷老五被打负伤，湘玉帮他清理伤口"}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "哎呀，轻点！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "郭芙蓉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "喝点热水吧！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "不用了，姑娘，水喝多了，不好钻洞。我跟你说，你容我准备准备，明天再，再比。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "郭芙蓉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "你都被打成这个模样了，你还想比啊？"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "就是。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "我这次输啊，是输在没经验上，我平时进的地方，就跟本没人开会——轻点儿，姑娘。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "哎呀，那你还真打算一直干这行啊！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "我都这把年纪了，学啥啥不灵，还改啥行啊？"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "那我不也改了吗？我说的是改正啊，不是改行。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "咱俩不一样，我要像你就好了，名气也有了，是吧，底也洗干净了，钱又不缺。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "谁说不缺，缺着呐！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "我不求别的，我走在街上，有人把我认出来，跟我要个签名什么的，我就知足了。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "村 民", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "请问……"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "郭芙蓉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "打烊了，打烊了！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "村 民", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "哎呀，不是吃饭，俺就想问你们这旮哒有个姓雷的吧？"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "啊？"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "你找他干什么？"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "村 民", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "我是个轿夫，左家庄的。这不，俺听说这雷老爷啊，通下水道可是一绝啊，专程来请他来了吗。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "你看我干啥呀，人又不找我。就这个，头破血流的这个雷老爷。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "村 民", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "哎呀妈呀，眼泪哗哗的，雷老爷啊，您方便吧，方便就跟俺去一趟呗？"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "现在啊？……"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "村 民", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "嗯呐。您不太方便吧？没关系，外头八抬大轿在正门口等您呢，我跟您说雷老爷，俺们村，锣鼓队，鞭炮队，还有开工酒，俺们庄的那老百姓张灯结彩都等着您呐，哎呀，您就去一回吧。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "那，那我就……"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "众人", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "去吧，去吧！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "郭芙蓉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "这是好事！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "为民排忧解难！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "佟湘玉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "行善积德！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "门口候着去！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "村 民", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "哎！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "各位，告辞了！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "等等，我那块牌子你不想要了？"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "speaker-action", "description": "摇头"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "这就对了，把那块匾额拿来！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "郭芙蓉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "好勒。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "哎哎哎，这不太合适，不合适，不合适……"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "你就拿着吧，这是你该得的，我要是有你这身本事，它还轮不着你呢！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "佟湘玉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "去吧去吧，过两天我们去慰劳你！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "啥也不说了！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "村 民", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "哎，我来我来，这事哪能劳烦雷老爷您呢，是不是？"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "雷老五", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "告辞！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "村 民", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "哎呀，雷老爷来了！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "终于逃过一劫呀！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "佟湘玉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "高兴个啥，他的牌子是拿走了，你的呢，还在衙门的匾额后面呢……"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "那就放那儿吧，放那儿总比放你身上安全。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "佟湘玉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "那可是你最宝贵的东西啊！"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "白展堂", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "以前是，现在对于我来说，最宝贵的——就是它，以后娶妻生子全靠它了。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "佟湘玉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "收好，不要让别人看见了。"}]}, {"type": "dialog", "speaker": "郭芙蓉", "performances": [{"type": "line", "line": "掌柜的，你敢跟我玩双重标准，店规二十三条规定，不准私受小费的，为什么老白可以，我就不可以呢？你跟我说清楚了……"}]}]}